## ğŸ” Whatâ€™s Inside

* **Theory-first notebook** explaining Agentic AI
* **ReAct-based agent** with an explicit execution loop
* **Single tool use case** (multiplier) to clearly show decision-making
* **Secure API key handling** (no hardcoding)

